long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TimeFlow is a Chrome extension that tracks time you spend on every website. It displays the result once you open a new browser tab. Have you ever wondered which website do you spend the most time on? Give it a try.
